       END PROGRAM SDF-TRANSLATE.



      *cOMBINATIONS

       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. COMBINE-ADD.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 D1 COMP-1.
       01 D2 COMP-1.
       01 R COMP-1.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING D1, D2, R.
       MAIN-PROCEDURE.
           COMPUTE R = FUNCTION MIN(D1, D2).
       END PROGRAM COMBINE-ADD.



       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. COMBINE-SUB.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 D1 COMP-1.
       01 D2 COMP-1.
       01 R COMP-1.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING D1, D2, R.
       MAIN-PROCEDURE.
           COMPUTE R = FUNCTION MAX(-1.0 * D1, D2).
       END PROGRAM COMBINE-SUB.



       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. COMBINE-INTERSECT.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 D1 COMP-1.
       01 D2 COMP-1.
       01 R COMP-1.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING D1, D2, R.
       MAIN-PROCEDURE.
